Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.04,0:01:44.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我…會死嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.11,0:01:51.61,Title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)\pos(210,550)}愛將征服一切。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.10,0:01:56.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}夜之愛子是能無限產生魔力的寶石
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.48,0:01:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但身體非常虛弱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.44,0:02:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}活著就會不斷重複吸收和產生魔力
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.74,0:02:08.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}最後身體會不堪重負
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.12,0:02:11.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你很清楚啊 愛麗絲
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.52,0:02:11.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.68,0:02:14.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}他放著身處危險的你不管
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.81,0:02:19.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}為了滿足他的好奇 放任地讓你活著
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.72,0:02:27.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那時的頭暈…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.04,0:02:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}智世 他沒有感情
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.01,0:02:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}他只是裝成人類的冒牌貨
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.11,0:02:38.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}別指望他會像人一樣愛你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.69,0:02:42.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你是他買下的 這是你無形的枷鎖
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.81,0:02:45.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}他還對你施了追蹤術
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.62,0:02:47.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你很痛苦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.26,0:02:55.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我們會幫你恢復自由
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.61,0:03:09.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}艾瑞爾
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.13,0:03:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}師父
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.79,0:03:18.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這裡是我們的地盤
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.38,0:03:20.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}魔術師不許在這裡惹事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.55,0:03:23.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你還好嗎 艾瑞爾
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.74,0:03:27.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯 離開鐵絲就沒事了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.05,0:03:30.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}為什麼 你不想要解脫嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.01,0:03:33.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}從哪裡解脫？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.44,0:03:38.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}如果你是指艾利亞斯 你恐怕不了解他
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.24,0:03:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}哪怕只是謊言 只有艾利亞斯稱我為家人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.13,0:03:47.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你說的是真是假都無所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.47,0:03:51.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}他比任何人還快就將我買下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.13,0:04:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}所以直到艾利亞斯放開我 我都是他的人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.06,0:04:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}愛麗絲
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.99,0:04:09.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不記得了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.01,0:04:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我是影子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.89,0:04:15.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}潛藏在荊棘之影下的人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.40,0:04:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你們稱我為裂噬之城
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.83,0:04:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}還好吧 智世
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.81,0:04:28.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.77,0:04:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}讓我看看傷口
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.20,0:04:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}傷口？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.94,0:04:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真亂來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.82,0:04:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}痛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.86,0:04:37.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}人類受了傷 很快就會死的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.26,0:04:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}來得太慢了 身為影子還這麼沒存在感
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.70,0:04:44.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}有智世在 我也沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.70,0:04:51.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}束縛快要解開了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.90,0:04:54.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}智世 這裡沒問題的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.36,0:04:56.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}麻煩你把這淨化了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.68,0:04:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.97,0:04:59.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我也同行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.64,0:05:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}國王
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.42,0:05:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不用擔心啦 是我和智世一起淨化呀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.42,0:05:08.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}如果這片汙穢能消失
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.77,0:05:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}身為國王 最後的責任就是見證這一切
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.07,0:05:13.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}沒錯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.35,0:06:01.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}智世 智世 你還好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.50,0:06:03.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這裡是？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.85,0:06:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}很久以前的小酒店 吃東西的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.64,0:06:10.09,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}鄰鎮可漂亮了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.56,0:06:12.48,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}聽說有好多美女啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.68,0:06:13.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}透明的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.94,0:06:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這裡好像是那片汙穢的記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.20,0:06:21.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那個人是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.04,0:06:27.04,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.15,0:06:38.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你就是漂泊的魔術師嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.78,0:06:45.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.49,0:06:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}看到是個小孩 有嚇到嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.27,0:06:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}有什麼要商量嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.95,0:06:52.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.38,0:06:56.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}旅行久了 總會有人找我幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.60,0:06:58.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}農作物歉收嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.81,0:07:01.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}還是想奪得女孩的歡心？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.31,0:07:04.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不是 我太太天生身體虛弱
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.95,0:07:10.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}總是臥病在床 我想讓她重獲健康
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.08,0:07:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}您有沒有什麼好藥呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.36,0:07:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}您真喜歡夫人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.98,0:07:19.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}當然啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.40,0:07:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}想都不想嗎 你挺羞澀的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.78,0:07:31.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}可以讓我見見夫人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.76,0:07:34.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}麻煩您了 請立刻來一趟
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.53,0:07:44.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}他不是個好人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.34,0:07:49.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}謝謝你 好好休息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.22,0:07:51.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我和您丈夫談一談
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.48,0:07:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好的 謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.78,0:08:00.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}請問 情況如何
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.66,0:08:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}提姆 提姆
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.76,0:08:08.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怎麼了 提姆
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.78,0:08:14.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}恐怕不會再有所好轉 只能活幾年了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.45,0:08:17.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這是天生的 沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.24,0:08:19.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怎麼會…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.01,0:08:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}米娜從小就不能出門玩耍
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.45,0:08:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}明明本性勤奮 卻因為體弱不得不臥床
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.53,0:08:31.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}她真的很可憐啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.50,0:08:33.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}只要是我能做到的事 我都願意去做
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.06,0:08:37.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}求你了 我真的不忍心看她這樣死去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.33,0:08:42.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}您夫人喜歡貓嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.05,0:08:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}貓？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.12,0:08:47.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.22,0:08:51.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是嗎 那倒是有一個辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.40,0:08:56.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你知道嗎 貓有九條命哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.62,0:09:02.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}又是老鼠嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.14,0:09:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}最近老鼠是不是變多了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.48,0:09:10.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}家貓們不會都在偷懶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.03,0:09:14.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}米娜 你出來走動不要緊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.13,0:09:20.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯 今天天氣也挺好的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.37,0:09:23.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}欸 你們看到馬修嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.58,0:09:26.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我剛才去送午餐 但他不在田裡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.67,0:09:30.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}說不定是去和哪個女人幽會了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.25,0:09:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}別胡說八道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.60,0:09:38.01,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}全村的人都知道馬修對米娜一心一意
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.01,0:09:38.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我剛才看到他拿著斧頭進了森林
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.19,0:09:40.01,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我開玩笑的啦 開玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.56,0:09:39.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}森林？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.18,0:09:55.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}馬修 馬修？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.82,0:10:05.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}智世 沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.90,0:10:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你臉色好差
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.44,0:10:11.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我有一種很不好的預感
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.74,0:10:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}房子？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.93,0:10:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}原來這裡還有間房子嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.23,0:10:42.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.90,0:10:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}馬修真是的 在這裡做什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.22,0:10:48.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}馬修
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.82,0:10:50.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.90,0:10:51.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}馬修
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.40,0:10:53.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.62,0:10:58.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不可以看裡面
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.47,0:11:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}馬修？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.89,0:11:27.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}米娜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.67,0:11:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你今天身體狀態不錯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.00,0:11:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}正好 我剛剛製作完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.88,0:11:48.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這是給你的藥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.09,0:11:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}藥？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.77,0:11:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}馬修 你在…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.34,0:11:54.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你在說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.78,0:11:57.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}之前不是讓魔術師看過病嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.76,0:12:00.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}他說只要做出這種靈藥給你服用
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.57,0:12:02.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}就能治好你的身體
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.92,0:12:07.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}貓呢 這些貓是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.61,0:12:09.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}都是材料
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.28,0:12:14.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}人們說貓有九條命 其實那是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.23,0:12:18.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}所以把貓的生命收集起來 就能做成靈藥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.32,0:12:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這種畜生居然有那麼多條命 真不公平
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.36,0:12:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}馬修 欸 馬修你怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.38,0:12:28.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}為什麼要做這麼殘忍的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.37,0:12:31.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你不是會做出這種事的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.18,0:12:33.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我做得出來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.08,0:12:40.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}因為都是為了你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.31,0:12:44.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}馬修
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.14,0:12:47.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}身體動不了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.15,0:12:51.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}沒事的 不用害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.60,0:12:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}喝下那個 你就能從不自由的身體中解放出來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.86,0:13:00.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不僅如此 還有可能獲得永久的壽命
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.60,0:13:03.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你…對馬修做了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.24,0:13:07.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}只是稍微取得信用而已
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.96,0:13:12.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}沒事的 這可是很棒的藥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.24,0:13:13.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}所以呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.40,0:13:18.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}來當我的小白鼠吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.71,0:13:35.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}米娜 不要緊的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.19,0:13:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}只有一開始會痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.40,0:13:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}忍耐一下 米娜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.27,0:13:42.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這樣就能獲得健康的身體了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.99,0:13:49.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我是幸運的 所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.65,0:13:54.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}馬修
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.21,0:14:24.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}失敗了嗎 身體崩壞掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.26,0:14:28.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}畜生終究只是畜生啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.01,0:14:30.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}就算比人類容易加工
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.16,0:14:33.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但本能很強 所以反噬的詛咒也更強
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.68,0:14:37.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}看來要先重新研究如何凝縮靈魂了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.32,0:14:40.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}謝謝你提供了寶貴的實驗結果 大哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.04,0:14:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.03,0:14:46.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.43,0:14:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}米娜 米娜 米娜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.12,0:14:53.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}為什麼米娜會…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.54,0:14:55.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}哎呀 壞掉了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.77,0:14:57.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}愛真是偉大啊 大姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.33,0:15:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}為什麼 為什麼 為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.44,0:15:04.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}為什麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.45,0:15:13.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}對了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.80,0:15:17.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}還不夠
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.30,0:15:25.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}還需要…更多更多更多的…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.06,0:15:27.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}必須收集更多才行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.38,0:15:31.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}要去收集 更多的…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.53,0:15:38.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}提姆 你來得正好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.42,0:15:42.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你最喜歡的米娜現在很不妙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.10,0:15:46.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}所以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.85,0:16:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你已經不再是人 變成惡魔了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.00,0:16:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}成了被惡魔欺騙的可憐惡魔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.46,0:16:10.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不能讓你活下去 也不能讓你安穩地死去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.37,0:16:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}因為我是牠們選出的王
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.43,0:16:15.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}也是為了那些死去的同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.68,0:16:21.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}米娜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.37,0:16:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}米娜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.06,0:16:28.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}米娜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.77,0:16:33.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}米娜在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.80,0:16:36.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你不在 我好寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.43,0:16:41.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}米娜 米娜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.03,0:16:50.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}智世
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.18,0:16:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}讓你看到不好的回憶了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.16,0:17:03.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}本來只想請你消除掉我們
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.45,0:17:06.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但你有很強的觀察力
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.78,0:17:08.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.72,0:17:16.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}「消除」是什麼意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.79,0:17:20.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}就是字面意思 讓我們消失
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.05,0:17:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}生物的靈魂終將回歸輪迴
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.83,0:17:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但是我和馬修都忘記了如何回歸輪迴
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.14,0:17:35.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那些貓也是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.89,0:17:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}貓…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.54,0:17:41.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}遭到殺害 許下詛咒的貓的靈魂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.79,0:17:46.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}大家都忘記了該如何回歸輪迴
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.19,0:17:52.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}所以希望你能消除掉我們
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.42,0:17:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我辦不到
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.82,0:17:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你們只是被欺騙了 不應該這樣消失
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.19,0:18:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不行 不可以的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.69,0:18:07.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}錯過這次 前方會有更無盡痛苦的黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.11,0:18:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}所以現在只有你能做到
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.98,0:18:14.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那就由我來做指引吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.17,0:18:15.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}國王
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.18,0:18:20.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這已是我的第九條命 不久將回歸塵土
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.71,0:18:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我的話 應該能指引你們前進的方向
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.52,0:18:28.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不行 絕對不行 那孩子會傷心的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.01,0:18:32.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}死亡總是突然又平等的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.55,0:18:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}或早或晚 終將來臨
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.55,0:18:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}剛才的王 還有之前的王
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.53,0:18:42.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}為了抑制汙穢 都獻上了自己的靈魂為祭
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.24,0:18:48.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這麼一想 指引一程就相對輕鬆多了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.72,0:18:51.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我擁有和那孩子的回憶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.53,0:18:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這樣就足夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.41,0:19:01.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.63,0:19:06.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}該怎麼辦…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.58,0:19:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}等等
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.44,0:19:15.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}艾瑞爾 你的話…用你的力量的話
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.68,0:19:18.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}用你能將花種送往千里之外的風…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.46,0:19:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.73,0:19:26.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}花種入土 落花為肥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.56,0:19:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}便是土地和風的盟約
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.97,0:19:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}該回歸輪迴的事物 就該回歸
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.09,0:19:35.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}人類真是 又傻又聰明又有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.80,0:19:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}所以我們無法離開你們
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.25,0:19:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我不會讓你消失的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.21,0:19:50.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}別擔心 她會帶你去的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.49,0:19:53.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}所以你也想像一下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.11,0:19:57.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}蒲公英的種子乘風而行的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.61,0:20:03.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}想像自己在那裡生根發芽
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.22,0:20:08.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}想像風兒帶著你前往應至的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.95,0:20:26.80,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5}目の前のその青に
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.07,0:20:33.70,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5}届かない事を知る
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.32,0:20:40.06,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5}同じ空見てたのに
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.39,0:20:45.61,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5}君は遠い雲
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.60,0:20:53.51,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5}夕暮れに月を探す
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.71,0:21:00.41,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5}行き先も知らないで
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.09,0:21:06.31,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5}いつかは覚める夢も
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.04,0:21:12.61,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5}思い出せるように
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.23,0:21:24.30,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5}空に流れ着いた
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.52,0:21:30.78,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5}手をつなぐ様に舞う花
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.08,0:21:37.61,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5}微かに聞こえている
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.73,0:21:45.42,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5}通じ合える言葉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.95,0:20:26.80,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5}眼前的那片蔚藍
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.07,0:20:33.70,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5}我知道自己捉摸不到
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.32,0:20:40.06,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5}明明望著同一片天空
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.39,0:20:45.61,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5}你卻是天邊那朵孤雲
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.60,0:20:53.51,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5}傍晚時分 我追尋著月亮
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.71,0:21:00.41,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5}漫無目標地四處奔走
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.09,0:21:06.31,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5}只希望回想起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.04,0:21:12.61,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5}那終將甦醒的夢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.23,0:21:24.30,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5}隨風飄蕩 飛向天際
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.52,0:21:30.78,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5}曼舞的花瓣 好像你我緊牽的手
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.08,0:21:37.61,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5}我聽見那輕輕的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.73,0:21:45.42,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5}是我們呢喃的愛語
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.20,0:20:58.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}馬修
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.37,0:21:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}米娜
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.17,0:21:06.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}馬修
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.99,0:21:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}米娜 你都跑哪去了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.89,0:21:22.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}馬修 走吧馬修
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.60,0:21:28.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}謝謝你 智世
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.06,0:21:31.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}親愛的小魔法使
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.67,0:21:37.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}希望你還不會來我們這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.69,0:21:59.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我原本是個沒人要的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.08,0:22:03.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}無人想收留我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.19,0:22:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}一次又一次被拋棄 掙扎為生
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.22,0:22:07.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}明明…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.09,0:22:16.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}終於找到了一個可能的巢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.49,0:22:22.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我什麼時候會死呢
Comment: 0,0:22:26.52,0:22:26.59,Default,,0,0,0,,ED-FF FINAL
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.56,0:22:44.95,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}枝に結ぶ　実が熟す前に
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.95,0:22:49.43,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}落ちてしまわぬよう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.35,0:22:57.52,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}苦しいほどに　また咲き乱れる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.66,0:23:02.64,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}朝へ　つなぐよう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.77,0:23:14.65,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}何度繰り返し　繰り返し　生まれても
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.45,0:23:28.09,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}いつも　新しい　空を見せてあげよう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.09,0:23:39.95,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}誰もまだ誰も　書いてない物語
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.44,0:23:54.26,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}白い　真っ白い地図に　描いてゆこう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.56,0:22:44.95,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}別不待結上枝頭 果實成熟
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.95,0:22:49.43,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}便早早飄落在地
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.35,0:22:57.52,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}越是風吹雨打 越要爛漫綻放
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.66,0:23:02.64,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}迎向嶄新的朝霞
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.77,0:23:14.65,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}一遍遍 又是一遍遍 你誕生在世
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.45,0:23:28.09,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}我依舊 會為你帶來 又一片藍天
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.09,0:23:39.95,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}是誰 又是誰 寫下嶄新的篇章
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.44,0:23:54.26,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}鋪開 純白的地圖 描繪軌跡 歌唱明天
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.17,0:24:00.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}指引靈魂的代價很大
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.81,0:24:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}墜入沉睡的少女和守護她的魔法使
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.06,0:24:07.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}出現在兩人面前的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.32,0:24:09.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}能介紹你的妻子給我嗎
